    "Title": "2022 OtH Winter Series #2 (Int, 40-49): 11th",
    "Image_File_Name": "oth-20220229.jpg",
    "Image_Display_Class": "postcard",
    "Image_File_Type": "image",
    "Intro": "<p> I didn't catch the first Winter Series race, but I was determined\r\n    not to miss the second. My result wasn't great, but I had fun, and\r\n    it renewed my motivation to trim off the fat that I've gained\r\n    ever-so-slowly over the last couple of years. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> I'm looking forward to race #3 on Feb 26, and I'm determined to\r\n    line up for the Summer Series on May 3 leaner & fitter than I've\r\n    been in years.\r\n</p>\r\n",
