    "Title": "Checking In",
    "Image_File_Name": "20180308-bike-trail.jpg",
    "Image_Display_Class": "postcard",
    "Image_File_Type": "image",
    "Intro": "<p> Life has been taking a bite out of my my workout schedule\r\n    recently. I've been getting workouts in when I can, but my last\r\n    actual trail ride was back in <a href=\"archive/3358\">2017</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> I have training goals, but first things first: I just want to get\r\n    back into a normal rhythm. For now, that means rest & get over a\r\n    chest cold. Near-term, I'd really like to be in shape to race in\r\n    the <a href=\"http://raceoc.com/\">OtH series</a> summer. Looks like\r\n    the races will kick off in about 8 weeks.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Lots to do between now and then. We'll see how this shakes out.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> (Photo originally taken <a href=\"archive/3242\">Feb 20, 2016</a>.)\r\n</p>\r\n",
