    "User_Name": "Chris",
    "Via_Title": null,
    "Title": "Garmin Screens",
    "Image_File_Name": "20170710-garmin.jpg",
    "Image_Display_Class": "postcard",
    "Image_File_Type": "image",
    "Intro": "<p> Once in a while I have to reset my Garmin, and every single time,\r\n    I wish I'd written down how I have my various screens set up.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> That ends today.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n",
    "Body": "<h3>Screen 1: Whole Ride</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n    <li> heart rate\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> average speed\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> current speed\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> total time\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> lap count\r\n    </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3>Screen 2: This Lap</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n    <li> heart rate\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> average speed (lap)\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> current speed\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> lap time\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> lap count\r\n    </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3>Screen 3: Interval Training</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n    <li> heart rate\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> lap time\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> cadence\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li> lap count\r\n    </li>\r\n</ol>",
    "Via_Text": null,
